verbose_text: Our laboratory has shown that CdsD, a unique protein orthologs to YscD that contains two fork-head associated domains, interacts with the predicted C. pneumoniae ATPase tethering protein, CdsL, as well as CdsQ, a putative multi-cargo transport protein.
